{
  "video_id": "w9tlEA7vuew",
  "title": "《哈 臺南》第八集：藝遊荷趣│《Hot Tainan》EP8. Recreation of Lotus Flowers",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 30675.0,
      "end_time": 31827.0,
      "text": "Hi, I’m Jacqueline."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 32275.0,
      "end_time": 35397.0,
      "text": "Can you believe that within these country roads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 35900.0,
      "end_time": 39740.0,
      "text": "there’s a pottery studio right there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 39475.0,
      "end_time": 40675.0,
      "text": "If you want to learn more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 40700.0,
      "end_time": 41725.0,
      "text": "let’s go check it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 41975.0,
      "end_time": 46750.0,
      "text": "Some people use cameras to take images of lotus flower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 46475.0,
      "end_time": 51160.0,
      "text": "and other people prefer to dye their fabrics with lotus petals."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 51550.0,
      "end_time": 55878.0,
      "text": "In addition, some artists draw lotus flowers on potteries"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 56225.0,
      "end_time": 60000.0,
      "text": "so that they exist beyond the limit of flower season."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 60475.0,
      "end_time": 64269.0,
      "text": "One interesting thing I would like to mention here is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 64575.0,
      "end_time": 68479.0,
      "text": "a lot of pottery works that you can see at Tainan city"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 68725.0,
      "end_time": 70699.0,
      "text": "come from this pottery studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 71200.0,
      "end_time": 73925.0,
      "text": "This pottery studio in Baihe"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 73950.0,
      "end_time": 77276.0,
      "text": "is founded by an artist called Lin Wen-yueh"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 77650.0,
      "end_time": 80225.0,
      "text": "Here he focuses on art creation"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 80325.0,
      "end_time": 83700.0,
      "text": "and exhibits his creations in his gallery."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 85750.0,
      "end_time": 88275.0,
      "text": "Wow! There are so many artworks here."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 88575.0,
      "end_time": 89983.0,
      "text": "There are Chinese painting"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 90250.0,
      "end_time": 92999.0,
      "text": "and calligraphy works as well as potteries."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 93200.0,
      "end_time": 95952.0,
      "text": "The vivid lotus flowers on the tea pot"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 96250.0,
      "end_time": 98234.0,
      "text": "look as if they are real."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 98400.0,
      "end_time": 100666.0,
      "text": "The calligraphy works on the wall"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 101100.0,
      "end_time": 104798.0,
      "text": "seem like they’re having a dialogue with the statues in front."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 105500.0,
      "end_time": 106521.0,
      "text": "It’s interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 108625.0,
      "end_time": 110275.0,
      "text": "Behind me is a kiln,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 110675.0,
      "end_time": 114977.0,
      "text": "and all those works we’ve just seen were made from this kiln."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 115475.0,
      "end_time": 118454.0,
      "text": "What’s so special about this kiln is that"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 118675.0,
      "end_time": 122131.0,
      "text": "they burn woods to heat up for making potteries."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 122550.0,
      "end_time": 124175.0,
      "text": "Among these artworks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 124250.0,
      "end_time": 126375.0,
      "text": "I saw a huge pottery work."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 126575.0,
      "end_time": 129633.0,
      "text": "Let’s find out which kiln it was made from."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 130125.0,
      "end_time": 132799.0,
      "text": "The work that we just saw in the studio"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 132799.0,
      "end_time": 135847.0,
      "text": "is  like two hundred and eleven centimeters."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 136150.0,
      "end_time": 137366.0,
      "text": "It’s so tall."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 137750.0,
      "end_time": 140500.0,
      "text": "In order to make such a big pottery work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 141000.0,
      "end_time": 144154.0,
      "text": "we also need a kiln that is big enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 144500.0,
      "end_time": 147124.0,
      "text": "to fit in this kind of pottery work."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 148000.0,
      "end_time": 152500.0,
      "text": "And so the kiln behind me has a rail way track"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 152425.0,
      "end_time": 156500.0,
      "text": "that can move and combine the kilns together."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 156575.0,
      "end_time": 160779.0,
      "text": "We happen to have the chance to see an artist creating his work."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 161450.0,
      "end_time": 164100.0,
      "text": "Some works have to be reassembled"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 164375.0,
      "end_time": 166448.0,
      "text": "after they’re copied by the mold."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 167225.0,
      "end_time": 168505.0,
      "text": "So, is this a lotus?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 168750.0,
      "end_time": 172231.0,
      "text": "This is a symbol of lotus."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 172400.0,
      "end_time": 173168.0,
      "text": "This work"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 173168.0,
      "end_time": 178119.0,
      "text": "is inspired by the saying “Lotus blooms untainted from the mud.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 178500.0,
      "end_time": 182299.0,
      "text": "We tried to transform this concept into symbols."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 182525.0,
      "end_time": 186493.0,
      "text": "It’s different from common realistic lotus artworks."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 186875.0,
      "end_time": 191291.0,
      "text": "Emerging oneself in the sounds of cicadas and breezes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 191650.0,
      "end_time": 195857.0,
      "text": "the artist creates his artworks in the wide-open nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 196175.0,
      "end_time": 198543.0,
      "text": "Maybe this is why people say"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 199000.0,
      "end_time": 202936.0,
      "text": "“As long as you remain calm, you don’t feel the heat.”"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 203100.0,
      "end_time": 207250.0,
      "text": "And by letting go of one’s worries and concerns,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 207175.0,
      "end_time": 209800.0,
      "text": "the artist can listen to his own thought"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 209925.0,
      "end_time": 212549.0,
      "text": "and infuse it into his creations."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 213500.0,
      "end_time": 215635.0,
      "text": "After you feel its power of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 215950.0,
      "end_time": 217230.0,
      "text": "you turn it into a piece of work"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 217600.0,
      "end_time": 218750.0,
      "text": "and then showcase it."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 218750.0,
      "end_time": 220542.0,
      "text": "You save it and then deliver it again."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 221425.0,
      "end_time": 223729.0,
      "text": "This is  so-called “the effect of beauty” in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 223850.0,
      "end_time": 226632.0,
      "text": "The transformation from one’s feeling towards"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 226632.0,
      "end_time": 229256.0,
      "text": "the nature to the creation of beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 229256.0,
      "end_time": 230728.0,
      "text": "is quite profound."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 230950.0,
      "end_time": 233317.0,
      "text": "Although you hear the sounds of insects"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 233318.0,
      "end_time": 235110.0,
      "text": "and chirps of birds here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 235300.0,
      "end_time": 237412.0,
      "text": "they actually calm you down."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 237600.0,
      "end_time": 239524.0,
      "text": "The artist put aside his work"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 239625.0,
      "end_time": 242313.0,
      "text": "and treated me to a cup of tea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 242425.0,
      "end_time": 244484.0,
      "text": "with the breeze passing through me."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244750.0,
      "end_time": 246851.0,
      "text": "We enjoyed the Zen lifestyle."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 247225.0,
      "end_time": 249757.0,
      "text": "Making friends through cups of tea"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 249850.0,
      "end_time": 251489.0,
      "text": "is probably like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 251850.0,
      "end_time": 253424.0,
      "text": "For example, we held the Shang-su Festival"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 253425.0,
      "end_time": 255130.0,
      "text": "which a variety of artists would come and join us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 255800.0,
      "end_time": 258625.0,
      "text": "including musicians and artists who know how to make tea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 258625.0,
      "end_time": 264897.0,
      "text": "and pottery artists,calligraphy artists, etc."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 266800.0,
      "end_time": 270400.0,
      "text": "I was impressed by one of the works in the gallery."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 270675.0,
      "end_time": 272575.0,
      "text": "What a huge pottery."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 272925.0,
      "end_time": 277575.0,
      "text": "It’s definitely a difficult task to biscuit fire the pottery."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 278450.0,
      "end_time": 279474.0,
      "text": "This work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 280500.0,
      "end_time": 282354.0,
      "text": "except for the time I spent on building the kiln and that space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 282750.0,
      "end_time": 284100.0,
      "text": "took me three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 285450.0,
      "end_time": 287640.0,
      "text": "Excluding style making,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 287850.0,
      "end_time": 289324.0,
      "text": "it stayed in the kiln for fifteen days"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 289324.0,
      "end_time": 290125.0,
      "text": "before I took it out again."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 290525.0,
      "end_time": 292974.0,
      "text": "The glaze applied to this pottery"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 292975.0,
      "end_time": 295430.0,
      "text": "is made of local materials:"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 295425.0,
      "end_time": 297985.0,
      "text": "mud from hot springs in Baihe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 298175.0,
      "end_time": 302657.0,
      "text": "limestone, and ash of lotus as well as longan trees."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 302975.0,
      "end_time": 306367.0,
      "text": "Together they make the most natural glaze."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 307100.0,
      "end_time": 308188.0,
      "text": "This upper layer"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 309100.0,
      "end_time": 310610.0,
      "text": "is made of wood."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 310150.0,
      "end_time": 314733.0,
      "text": "We can draw it on the pottery due to its thick and pure texture."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 315575.0,
      "end_time": 317366.0,
      "text": "It took me great work"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 317367.0,
      "end_time": 319290.0,
      "text": "to finish this fundamental research."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 321375.0,
      "end_time": 325196.0,
      "text": "After spending like a half day here at this studio"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 325275.0,
      "end_time": 327275.0,
      "text": "And after drinking a cup of tea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 327775.0,
      "end_time": 329820.0,
      "text": "I feel like I’m totally relaxed."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 330400.0,
      "end_time": 333950.0,
      "text": "And I think life is not so difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 334175.0,
      "end_time": 336874.0,
      "text": "It’s just the way how we think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 337700.0,
      "end_time": 342460.0,
      "text": "So I think maybe life is not so complicated as we thought."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 342800.0,
      "end_time": 347132.0,
      "text": "And now I have more courage to face the difficulties"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 347132.0,
      "end_time": 348444.0,
      "text": "I am dealing with now."
    }
  ]
}